title: Ep - 71 - Big Brother's Elena Davies and Mark Jansen
description:
Elena Davies and Mark Jansen competed against each other during season 19 of Big Brother and ultimately fell in love. They discuss what it is like to be a contestant on the show, how they are still trying to get acclimated to life outside of isolation, and figuring out their careers post show. 


Tyler Baltierra is an MTV personality who appeared on the show Teen Mom alongside his pregnant girlfriend (now wife), Catelynn Lowell. Kate forced him to watch this week’s episode of Real Housewives of Orange County. 


Jeffrey Williamson is a photographer, social media guru and media (tv, music, movie) lover. He is co-host of the popular culture podcast “The Pop Tea Podcast”. Jeffrey forced Kate to watch Love & Hip Hop New York. 


Reality Life with Kate Casey
